---
title: Honey and Orange Chicken Jambalaya with Tomato Rice
description: Jambalaya is a traditional Creole dish with rice, tomatoes, onions, green peppers, and some type of protein. Our chefs put a family-friendly spin on the dish by adding orange zest for a burst of citrus flavor and honey to balance out the acidity of the tomatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-chicken-jambalaya-family-718aa474.jpg
